A buff (/shock shiver panic)<br>
But nothing along the lines of AC, hp, or any other non-wizardly shitz. I'm thinking about a buff that would act similarily to a cleric's spell Death Pact, in that there would be a chance it would evac the person to intra-zone location (or other), if they died, saving experience loss.<br>
I can see how people would want a wizard for this role, as the masters of arcane teleportation we should be able to evac more safely and in more creative ways then druids. <br>
My idea is this spell would be cast in deep dungeons so that, if you say missed a person in an evac or they died too quickly they would have a chance of escaping alive, avoiding nasty CR.<br>
What do you guys think about this idea?<br>
<br>
-Aleolin Darkmoon<br>
